Use amrex_particles_vtp.py as

    python amrex_particles_vtp.py <minfilenum> <maxfilenum> fileprefix

Example:

    python amrex_particles_vtp.py 0 2 samplefiles/particles

For amrex_binary_particles_to_vtp.py, do:

    python amrex_binary_particles_to_vtp.py plotfilename particle_type

Example:

    python amrex_binary_particles_to_vtp.py plt000354 DM            

The vtp files are written in the folder where the amrex particle files reside. 
